original: Some of these songs are featured in the film include the Lagani song, Sohar (birth song) and marriage songs like the Dahakan song, Bariya song and the Parichan song.

original: Do you know a Kagzi Mohalla exists in the heart of Rajasthan?

original: The pole is then placed over a hollow bamboo tube which is six to seven inches tall worn around the waist during the performance.
translation: पोळ्याचा एक भाग एका पोकळ बांबूच्या ट्यूबवर ठेवला जातो, जो प्रदर्शनादरम्यान कमरेभोवती 6 ते 7 इंच उंचीचा असतो.

original: Served in a paper cone called Thonga, the main ingredients in this dish are puffed rice mixed with spicy chickpea (Chana chur), Sev-puri-namkeen, onion, chilli and tomato.
translation: थोंगा नावाच्या कागदी शंकूवर सर्व्ह केलेले, या डिशमधील मुख्य घटक मसालेदार चणे (चणे चूर), सेवन-पूरी-नमकीन, कांदा, मिरची आणि टोमॅटो मिसळून बनवलेले तांदूळ आहेत.

original: Cluster headaches usually happen every day, in bouts lasting several weeks or months at a time (typically 4 to 12 weeks), before they subside.
translation: क्लस्टर डोकेदुखी सहसा दररोज होते, अनेक आठवडे किंवा महिने एका वेळी (सामान्यतः 4 ते 12 आठवडे), ते कमी होण्यापूर्वी.

original: Commonly known spices such as cumin, coriander, pepper, chillies, cardamom, cinnamon and cloves are used.

original: The PUBLISHER shall render to the AUTHOR, an yearly account of sales, commencing one year after the date of first publication and shall pay to the AUTHOR the amount becoming due under this Agreement within three months after the rendering of an yearly account.
translation: प्रकाशक पहिल्या प्रकाशनाच्या तारखेपासून एक वर्षानंतर वार्षिक विक्री लेखाजोखा प्राधिकरणाला देईल आणि वार्षिक लेखा सादर केल्यानंतर तीन महिन्यांच्या आत या करारांतर्गत देय रक्कम प्राधिकरणाला देईल.

original: It was inscribed in the UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage list in the year 2010 and is the second art form from the state to be inscribed in this list.
translation: २०१० साली युनेस्कोच्या अमूर्त सांस्कृतिक वारसा यादीत हे नाव समाविष्ट करण्यात आले आणि या यादीत समाविष्ट होणारे राज्यातील हे दुसरे कला स्वरूप आहे.

translation: मुनी की रेती शहरातील चंद्रेश्वर नगर येथील 7.5 एमएलडी सांडपाणी प्रक्रिया प्रकल्प हा देशातील पहिला 4 मजली सांडपाणी प्रक्रिया प्रकल्प असेल जिथे जमिनीची उपलब्धता मर्यादेचे संधीत रुपांतर करण्यात आले.

original: Also drinking too much alcohol raises blood pressure over time and makes heart failure worse.

original: Speaking on the occasion, the Prime Minister said during the last one and half years from the start of Jal Jeevan Mission more than 2 crore 60 lakh families have been provided piped drinking water connection to their homes including lakhs of families in Uttar Pradesh as well.

original: Like all medicines, morphine can cause side effects in some people but many people have no side effects or only minor ones.

original: Noting the increasing vibrancy of the agri-sector, Shri Modi talked of new alternative available to the farmers to sell their produce outside the mandis, modernization of mandis and option of selling produce on electronic platform.

original: Holding the meat skywards, all of a sudden, what was till then a cloudless sunny Jodhpur sky, gets filled with a convocation of Eagles bolting from all across the sky.

original: A plucked instrument of the lute category, it is majorly used in North Indian Classical music.

original: Costochondritis can be aggravated by any activity that places stress on your chest area, such as strenuous exercise or even simple movements like reaching up to a high cupboard.

original: Its aesthetic appeal was so great that the then Nawab of Golconda, Abdul Hasan Tanishah issued a copper plate in 1675 A.D. granting the village Kuchipudi as an Agrahaarama to the families of Brahmins who pursued this art.

original: It included coins struck by the Greek, lndo-Greek, Saka-Pahlava, Parthian, Kushana and Sassanian kings besides tribal coins of ancient India, Gupta coins, the coins of the Hindu kings of Ohind and Muhammedan coins of a large variety.
translation: यामध्ये ग्रीक, इंडो-ग्रीक, साका-पहलवा, पार्थियन, कुषाण आणि सास्सानियन राजांनी मुद्रित केलेली नाणी तसेच प्राचीन भारतातील आदिवासी नाणी, गुप्त नाणी, ओहिंदच्या हिंदू राजांची नाणी आणि विविध प्रकारच्या मुस्लीम नाणी यांचा समावेश होता.
